   <p><placeName ref="cwgk:P00001851">North Middletown</placeName>
<lb/><placeName ref="cwgk:P00000515">Bourbon Co Ky
</placeName>
<lb/><date when="1860-12-04">Decr 4. 1860</date>
<lb/>To his Excellency
<lb/><persName ref="cwgk:N00000258">Beriah Magoffin</persName><lb/>Govenor of Ky.</p>
<p>I hereby tender my resignation as Justice of the Peace for said county in District N<hi rend="underline"><hi rend="sup">o</hi></hi> 4. &amp; Recommend <persName ref="cwgk:N00001852">William R Gorham</persName> as a fit &amp; suitable person to fill my place.</p>
<p>verry Resp:
 <lb/><persName ref="cwgk:N00001853"><hi rend="underline">Ben F Harris</hi></persName></p>
<p>we citizens of said Precinct also endorse the Recommendation of said Harris</p>
<p><persName ref="cwgk:N00001854">B. F. Hart</persName>
<lb/><persName ref="cwgk:N00001855">J B Rankins</persName>
<lb/><persName ref="cwgk:N00001856">Joseph Scott</persName><pb/></p>
<p>Issue Commission
<lb/>B. M</p>
  </body>
